modName: FalmerBanes - Dralora of Vivec - A Dunmer Companion
summary: Dralora is an attractive Dunmer companion that is located at her own camp sight west of Whiterun. She is available in 10 variations and all are set essential and will auto-level from 20 to 86 with the player. The included lore friendly campsite adds two safe player storage containers, a hot spring area as well as a cooking spit.
